---
title: Tofu & Veggie Brown Rice Poke Bowl with Toasted Sesame Dressing & Pickled Cucumber
description: We love poke bowls, because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This plant-based version uses
Peking-style tofu, brown rice, baby broccoli, carrot and cucumber, with a nutty sesame dressing to tie the whole thing together.

